00:09:46.460 --> 00:09:49.099
And, but God's okay with that, amen?

00:09:49.099 --> 00:09:51.780
And I was sitting here praying early this morning,

00:09:51.780 --> 00:09:53.099
and I was praying for each one of you

00:09:53.099 --> 00:09:55.700
by name this morning and praying that God would work

00:09:55.700 --> 00:09:57.539
