00:09:57.539 --> 00:09:59.179
And I began to pray for the young people

00:09:59.179 --> 00:10:00.020
as they sit.

00:10:00.020 --> 00:10:02.880
near the front and I began to pray that God would use them

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:05.340
and maybe they would be the catalyst

00:10:05.340 --> 00:10:08.700
that God would use to bring some revival.

00:10:10.340 --> 00:10:12.540
It was just a little lad that gave his lunch

00:10:12.540 --> 00:10:14.260
