00:10:30.900 --> 00:10:33.500
with regard to the work and to repair the house of the Lord

00:10:33.500 --> 00:10:35.380
and it says that when they brought out the money

00:10:35.380 --> 00:10:37.580
that was brought into the house of the Lord,

00:10:37.580 --> 00:10:41.540
Hilkiah the priest found a book of the law of the Lord

00:10:41.540 --> 00:10:43.100
