00:11:16.360 --> 00:11:19.840
that Shaphan read it, the book that was found

00:11:19.840 --> 00:11:23.440
in the house of the Lord before the king.

00:11:23.440 --> 00:11:26.600
We know the book, the Bible tells us in verse number 14

00:11:26.600 --> 00:11:29.440
