00:12:24.920 --> 00:12:27.320
the son of Shaphan and Abdon, the son of Micah,

00:12:27.320 --> 00:12:29.840
and Shaphan the scribe and Esaias, servant of the king,

00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:32.080
